It's a little hard to make large
scale changes to all the buttons.

234
00:12:58.187 --> 00:13:00.872
Yes.
But if you're using enough variables and

235
00:13:00.872 --> 00:13:04.347
stuff like that, or you're really
fancy with your select all and

236
00:13:04.347 --> 00:13:07.144
renaming and stuff like that,
