00:13:07.144 --> 00:13:10.533
And that's typically what we ended up
doing even though we started down the path

238
00:13:10.533 --> 00:13:13.074
of trying to overload variance
with everything possible.

239
00:13:13.074 --> 00:13:16.572
So my advice to you is use them for
the simplest possible thing,

